    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed honestly as a fair-condition car, and buyers should have realistic expectations before purchasing. The exterior shows moderate wear including some dents, scratches, and paint fading consistent with regular daily use over the years. The interior is functional but shows signs of age \u2014 expect worn upholstery, some scuffs on trim panels, and general cosmetic fatigue. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it may benefit from some maintenance attention in the near term; we recommend a pre-purchase inspection so you know exactly what you're getting. This is a practical, drivable vehicle suited for a buyer who wants transportation at a fair price and is comfortable with a car that isn't perfect. No major hidden surprises \u2014 what you see is what you get.",
      "price": 16000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
